16.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers the sum that the travel organiser may demand be
paid to cancel the journey, as well as previously paid expenses for
deposits, transport, rent of holiday residence etc.
.br
The insurance only covers sums that the insured has paid himself/herself.
.sp 3mm
