:FED
17.0 Replacement employee
:SKRSLUT.
.br
:SWISS8.
Insurance sum: DKK 50,000 1 person.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
17.1 Coverage
:SKRSLUT.
.br
This insurance covers necessary and reasonable extra expenses for
travel, hotel and accommodation that the insured's company incurs from
posting a new employee when the originally posted employee has died or
been struck by a sudden and serious illness/injury that requires
hospitalisation during at least five days, or repatriation. The
hospitalisation and repatriation must be prescribed by a doctor and
agreed with SOS.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
17.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers up to DKK 50,000 in documented travel expenses
according to original receipts, although no more than the cost of travel
on an ordinary scheduled flight. Hotel and meals are covered in the
amount of DKK 1,800 per day.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
